        <updateDate>2021-06-01T14:04:32Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p>This bill makes permanent&nbsp;the Money Follows the Person Rebalancing Demonstration Program. Under this program, the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services may award grants to state Medicaid programs to assist states in increasing the use of home and community care for long-term care and decreasing the use of institutional care.</p> <p><br /></p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
